<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">附錄</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">懷感韻詩二</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0951b" n="0951b"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0951b01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="28"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="28"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="28"><cb:jhead>御製秘藏詮懷感一百韻詩卷第二十八<note place="inline">卷上</note>　<g ref="#CB01524">𦘺</g></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="K" n="0951b02"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">懷感韻詩三</cb:mulu><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b0201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">卜年興我運</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b0206" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">昔在成王定鼎郟鄏卜世三十卜年七百文王以文德被
<lb ed="K" n="0951b03"/>物武王以武功定亂致萬彚咸寧百靈受賜道齊天地德光日月遂使慶延三十七王祚
<lb ed="K" n="0951b04"/>永八百餘祀是知聖人之道今昔皆同捿神堯舜之前求治禹湯之上卜年興運成萬世
<lb ed="K" n="0951b05"/>之基又何姬周之年可為儔匹矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b0514" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">化洽等無疆</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b0519" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">天地所以能長且久
<lb ed="K" n="0951b06"/>者以其覆載無私功用不宰是以帝王法而行之使信及豚魚恩霑動植人躋富壽化復
<lb ed="K" n="0951b07"/>淳和自然無疆之休可大之德與夫南山之固北海之深不可得而優劣也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b0730" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">肅穆
<lb ed="K" n="0951b08"/>皆通濟</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b0804" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">華夷大同車書混一遽使暘谷東廻流沙西入南歸卉服北走穹廬
<lb ed="K" n="0951b09"/>通<g ref="#CB08866">󲊢</g>惠民既安且樂千里不齎於粮食四時自順於風雨肅恭不渝穆清仍著見帝王之
<lb ed="K" n="0951b10"/>用心在通濟而化物也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b1010" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">公平振紀綱</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b1015" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">仲<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>所謂必也正名乎者即是
<lb ed="K" n="0951b11"/>設官分職各有司存使滅私徇公措枉舉直振滯為理臨事有断若綱在綱有條而不紊
<lb ed="K" n="0951b12"/>則可以憲章文物拯濟黎元公平之道斯亦大矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b1220" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">清朝遵禮讓</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0951b13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b1301" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">朝有多士野無遺賢眀禮惟安上治民非王帛之為貴克讓乃益謙保德知鬼神之害盈
<lb ed="K" n="0951b14"/>此蓋上行三代之風下遵五常之道自然而然可謂又盡善矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b1425" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">眀德遠馨
<lb ed="K" n="0951b15"/>香</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b1502" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">老子云明白四照能無知乎則是至明之德燭萬物而察百姓合兩曜而順二儀尚
<lb ed="K" n="0951b16"/>書云至治馨香感于神明黍稷非馨明德惟馨又大易云東鄰殺牛不如西鄰之禴祭實
<lb ed="K" n="0951b17"/>受其福亦取於明德之義也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b1712" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">撫育同千古</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b1717" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">天生蒸民樹之司收又天
<lb ed="K" n="0951b18"/>地之大德日生此欲令聖人皆孩之如慈母之念嬰兒也然百王之下千古<anchor xml:id="beg_117" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_117"/>還子育大
<lb ed="K" n="0951b19"/>同而物遂其冝人受其惠何有於今之時哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951b1918" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">恩臨溥萬方</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951b1923" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">夫致地平
<lb ed="K" n="0951b20"/>天成者蓋德廣恩溥也亦如陽春發生蕭蘭俱澤故知帝德廣運無黨無偏使六合葵向
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0951c" n="0951c"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0951c01"/>萬方星拱豈難也哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0109" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">從容安世俗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0114" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">寬刑薄賦<g ref="#CB00421">䘏</g>寡賑貧聖政日隆則從
<lb ed="K" n="0951c02"/>容之治也尸無夜閇犬不宵鳴萬國詠謌即安世俗之明化也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0225" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">滌蕩順陰
<lb ed="K" n="0951c03"/>陽</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0302" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">左傳曰過而能改善莫大焉若乃生民有瑕亦冝洗蕩持賞罰之權柄順陰陽之唘
<lb ed="K" n="0951c04"/>闔凡曰有過皆得自新</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0410" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">喜色浮丹闕</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0415" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">丹闕乃王者之所居喜色
<lb ed="K" n="0951c05"/>則庶民之所樂國人既泰慶雲乃生浮非煙之祥暎丹闕之上</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0525" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">英聲徧八
<lb ed="K" n="0951c06"/>荒</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0602" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">民歌有道四方既仰於英聲化洽無垠八荒自歸於正朔八荒者東西南北四維荒
<lb ed="K" n="0951c07"/>服之外聲教所不到處也雖昔時未順而今乃咸賔矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0722" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">擇賢齊舜
<lb ed="K" n="0951c08"/>禹</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0802" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">舜自仄陋而求禹當昌言必拜搜擇賢善同致成平迨皇朝徵舉才能超拔英彥草
<lb ed="K" n="0951c09"/>澤之士咸出無愧於舜禹者哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c0913" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">簡易習堯唐</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c0918" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">瑞栱之化既成簡易
<lb ed="K" n="0951c10"/>之道斯著民皆胥樂物盡雍熙政化習於唐堯庶事和於太古</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1025" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">得意乹坤
<lb ed="K" n="0951c11"/>朗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1102" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖人設教四海恱隨法天而行順時而動得化民之意故天地而清朗焉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1130" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">慈和
<lb ed="K" n="0951c12"/>雨露滂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1204" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">宣慈惠和聖人之德也雨露渥澤聖人之恩也物<anchor xml:id="beg_118" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_118"/>從其教令澤必
<lb ed="K" n="0951c13"/>及於生靈肆赦眚災比雨露之滂霈也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1316" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">彌隆輝麗日</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1321" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">杲日麗天輝照
<lb ed="K" n="0951c14"/>六合之內皇風周普彌隆八表之中覆育之功照臨之德緣情抒思得不美乎</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1431" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">正治
<lb ed="K" n="0951c15"/>美甘棠</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1504" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">毛詩云蔽苐甘棠勿翦勿伐蓋美邵伯之教明於南國欲使居<g ref="#CB05729">𧂉</g>聞
<lb ed="K" n="0951c16"/>者絕其私在經濟者奉其政徵其前古以誡今來咸令化洽萬方同邵公之治民思不絕
<lb ed="K" n="0951c17"/>者</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1702" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">武藝皆奇絕</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1707" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">武者蓋欲遏禍威遠安民和眾者也故湏精鍊
<lb ed="K" n="0951c18"/>貔貅號令進退既皆奇絕復善機冝七德之功克全一戎衣而大定矣仲<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>云不教民戰
<lb ed="K" n="0951c19"/>是謂弃之也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c1906" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">英聲雅不狂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c1911" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">夫善用兵者盖果於不得<anchor xml:id="beg_119" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_119"/>且如前
<lb ed="K" n="0951c20"/><g ref="#CB07532">󱵬</g>來侵故用兵而止之故不取威黷武然後為勝矣所以英聲雖振雅正不渝此乃神武
<lb ed="K" n="0951c21"/>之道在乎手矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0951c2107" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">和平關塞靜</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0951c2112" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">一德用康九功惟序度開之吏曉征
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0952a" n="0952a"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a01"/>豈待於鷄鳴防塞之夫夜寢不虞於犬吠蕩蕩之化民共樂推</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0125" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">健羨野民
<lb ed="K" n="0952a02"/>康</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0202" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">東皐南畝春生秋成家有餘糧戶無煩伇鑿井而飲擊壤而歌豈知上有堯舜之君
<lb ed="K" n="0952a03"/>下有稷高之相沐浴聖化堪健羨哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0315" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">瑞播卿雲匝</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0320" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">九苞儀鳳皆呈瑞於
<lb ed="K" n="0952a04"/>皇都五色卿雲盡舒祥於帝闕乂安天下有斯昭著者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0423" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">書觀乙夜忙</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a05"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0501" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">宵衣待且乙夜觀書欲使品物昭蘇盡服淳和之化矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0522" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">鳬趨金殿政</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0601" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">一人凝旒百辟在列珠簾卷而香籠雉扇金殿肅而風清鳳旗共罄鳬趍同瞻堯彩也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a07"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">鼇抃玉<g ref="#CB00092">𡎰</g>傍</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0706" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">星拱葵向之方梯山航海之國來從遐<g ref="#CB00509">𧜟</g>未識大君同四
<lb ed="K" n="0952a08"/>隩之奉圖若百獸之率舞玉<g ref="#CB00092">𡎰</g>之下鼇抃而前帝德使然物自知化矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a0828" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">逈堡休
<lb ed="K" n="0952a09"/>烽燧</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a0903" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">太陽既升四極皆照況邊城逈堡荒俗遐陬豈敢拒於皇威而不從風教
<lb ed="K" n="0952a10"/>者哉所以烽燧罷警関防不虞民人用安康莊如<g ref="#CB10614">󲥶</g>也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1022" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">邊兵戢虎狼</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a11"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1101" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">如虎之師似狼之旅所向皆剋舉無失時今既歸馬休牛修文偃武春耕之俗徹榆塞以
<lb ed="K" n="0952a12"/>謳歌冬獵之徒逾燕山而馳騁蓋蠢尓之虜<anchor xml:id="beg_11a" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_11a"/>悛惡矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1222" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">戎夷思德義</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a13"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1301" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">東夷西戎懷德服義既營宮而望幸故稽領以推誠也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1322" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">蠻貊奉梯航</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952a14"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1401" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">舜帝格於三苗宣王征於六月蓋討其不順伐其為祓今既聲教大同德澤咸被梯航入
<lb ed="K" n="0952a15"/>貢府無虛月矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1507" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">治國三才順</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1512" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">以欲從人順時設教天地不迷於風雨民
<lb ed="K" n="0952a16"/>人皆稟於義方符瑞日臻鴻圖可久矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1616" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">雄文五色章</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1621" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">昔自兩漢逮于
<lb ed="K" n="0952a17"/>巨唐或五色之筆夢傳或一聯之詩神受然後聲塵煥尓文章蔚然今我后復三代之質
<lb ed="K" n="0952a18"/>文暢二南之雅道徵賈<g ref="#CB12607">𧨏</g>於宣室待相如於甘泉崇學尚儒去奢克儉文德之威未有如
<lb ed="K" n="0952a19"/>今之朝矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a1905" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">遐邇傳富庶</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a1910" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">德教大敷法被天下家<g ref="#CB01524">𦘺</g>國富遐邇覃恩皆傳
<lb ed="K" n="0952a20"/>元首明哉股肱良哉庶事康哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a2013" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">中外盡昭彰</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952a2018" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">每以至德要道垂教中區
<lb ed="K" n="0952a21"/>由是八表輸誠四夷入貢盡於等降禮待無遺以至萬國昭彰恭事上帝</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952a2129" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">墜典
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0952b" n="0952b"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0952b01"/>冝常補</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0104" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">體國經野以教為本化民成俗以學為先故墜典必修無文咸袟風
<lb ed="K" n="0952b02"/>行諸夏草偃殊服</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0208" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">玄機理不忘</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0213" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">機者動之微非聖人不能見即宏壽
<lb ed="K" n="0952b03"/>妙略理國幽致勳臣元輔精究寧忘故呂望師周禹湯佐舜盡得昇平矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0329" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">北燕窮
<lb ed="K" n="0952b04"/>毳幕</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0403" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">胡地玄冰邊土慘裂韋韝毳幕以禦風雨驅羊牧馬以資事業故聲教絕
<lb ed="K" n="0952b05"/>被篾有典墳</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0506" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">南地足菰蔣</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0511" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">島渚煩蒸魚塩成俗湖漅卑濕菰蔣
<lb ed="K" n="0952b06"/>復多蓋風土所冝方物自定比我上國氣<g ref="#CB07419">𠋫</g>懸殊</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0620" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">氣爽煙霞麗</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0625" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">中原
<lb ed="K" n="0952b07"/>景麗諸夏觀光五風信符十雨氣爽非煙羃羃彤麗依依丹鳳既集祥麟自現神龍攸降
<lb ed="K" n="0952b08"/>瑞龜斯出</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0805" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">鴻飛羽翼張</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b0810" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">毛詩云大曰鴻小曰<g ref="#CB13465">󳒙</g>文武面序猶鴻<g ref="#CB13465">󳒙</g>
<lb ed="K" n="0952b09"/>之行飛羽翼高張贊皇猷之永遠咸遵古道共致昇平</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b0922" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">閑情空縹緲</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952b10"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1001" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">天下無事國用益充曠然端拱之風豁尓凝旒之化致象外之志縹緲蓋域中之俗淳和
<lb ed="K" n="0952b11"/>矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1102" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">逸志自汪洋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1107" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">逸豫之情所以汪洋無際者聖人之心同天覆之大
<lb ed="K" n="0952b12"/>地載之廣子育之惠又何所不至哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1215" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em"><anchor xml:id="beg_11b" type="cb-app"/>豐<anchor xml:id="end_11b"/>稔連遐土</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1220" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">海隅之俗夷壤之民
<lb ed="K" n="0952b13"/>德化所臨風教所被既却走馬自糞田園則八稻嘉禾率土而豐稔矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1328" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">謳謌
<lb ed="K" n="0952b14"/>頌廣塲</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1404" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">國家所以闢文闈設太學思求寒後重抑世家用擇棟梁同康黎庶
<lb ed="K" n="0952b15"/>既咸臻於多士不求備於一人公道大開頌聲爰振</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1521" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">遂心收逆壘</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1526" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">堯舜
<lb ed="K" n="0952b16"/>在上周邵作弼縱使<g ref="#CB07140">󱯤</g>尤之旅有扈之徒以不能施武勇恣狂悖故菆尓之眾逆壘自平
<lb ed="K" n="0952b17"/>此蓋天人合功遂心而收矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1712" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">銜璧負牽羊</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1717" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">夫中原之君威臨萬
<lb ed="K" n="0952b18"/>國或銜璧而歸命或牽羊而納<g ref="#CB29376">󷋀</g>斯蓋悟偷生之不永遂歸化以求安</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b1828" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">舉動
<lb ed="K" n="0952b19"/>民皆樂</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b1904" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖人以欲從人慮一夫不獲舉事必求於康濟出言湏益於生靈致
<lb ed="K" n="0952b20"/>民忻戴樂推情不能<anchor xml:id="beg_11c" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_11c"/></note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b2010" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">雍容物不傷</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952b2015" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">不嚴而治不肅而成者蓋至仁
<lb ed="K" n="0952b21"/>守於雌靜務安萬物草木不殺飛走咸遂雍容居尊如日可受</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952b2125" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">郊禋陳簠
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0952c" n="0952c"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0952c01"/>簋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0102" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">車服<anchor xml:id="beg_11d" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_11d"/>備宗祀郊禋牢醴既修湏陳簠簋表聖心之肅穆法上古之規儀</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0130" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">班序
<lb ed="K" n="0952c02"/>儼珪璋</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0204" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">群臣班瑞儼列珪璋盡恭謹之心表精純之至則可以上天降祐也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952c03"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">覆載從<g ref="#CB15210">󳭪</g>廓</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0306" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">天覆地載育物無私類明君之風化也澤及昆蟲無
<lb ed="K" n="0952c04"/>黨無偏可謂<g ref="#CB15210">󳭪</g>廓矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0409" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">周流任渺茫</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0414" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">地雖無疆至德咸被所以物遂情性
<lb ed="K" n="0952c05"/>任其周流然不離於聖化也亦如百川奔注萬派渺茫同其朝宗皆歸海也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0530" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">歲時
<lb ed="K" n="0952c06"/>朋聖曆</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0604" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖曆既眀歲時爰定此乃察璿璣而調玉燭考短長而定盈虛使風
<lb ed="K" n="0952c07"/>雨不迷陰陽克叶者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0710" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">号令若嚴霜</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0715" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">發号施令懲姦止惡聖意
<lb ed="K" n="0952c08"/>在敷於德教民心稟若於嚴霜蓋匪滋章欲知賞罰矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c0822" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">蜀棧遊青嶺</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0952c09"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c0901" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">昔人言蜀道之難棧路之險今車馬遊往貢輸相望縱山之高嶺之峻人之履踐如<g ref="#CB10614">󲥶</g>者
<lb ed="K" n="0952c10"/>乃帝德使然無遠不至是知在德不在險也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1018" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">荊湘貢白麞</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1023" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">夫為瑞者
<lb ed="K" n="0952c11"/>隨時所出皆楨祥也今荊楚大澤產此白麞馴擾安處逼之不懼撫之不驚獲而貢之式
<lb ed="K" n="0952c12"/>光盛德又何必五色表奇一角稱異者哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1217" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">高風躋五帝</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1222" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">無為道著淳朴
<lb ed="K" n="0952c13"/>風清體天之義既眀則民之心咸服化同五帝可以高攀矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1324" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">盛德踵三
<lb ed="K" n="0952c14"/>皇</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1402" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">伏羲神農黃帝謂之三皇今則天下大定率土來賔紹卜年卜世之基継超三邁五
<lb ed="K" n="0952c15"/>之代矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1504" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">秘閣摽圖史</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1509" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蘭臺仙署麟閣石渠藏百代之筞書修前王之
<lb ed="K" n="0952c16"/>墜典瘴惡彰善俱有否臧矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1612" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">掄材選棟梁</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1617" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">有安邦之業懷經濟之才
<lb ed="K" n="0952c17"/>應運而生為時而出上可以股肱王室下可以康濟生民隨其所能掄材擢用</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1731" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">賑貧
<lb ed="K" n="0952c18"/>施穀麥</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1804" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">月令季春天子乃命有司發倉廩賜貧窮賑乏絕我國家應天順民
<lb ed="K" n="0952c19"/>受命踐祚師考古道也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c1910" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">貌儼見周姜</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c1915" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">周公為政子牙師傳功能代天
<lb ed="K" n="0952c20"/>力能舉國外肅敦仁之貌內懷臣莭之心今之賢輔可比用善矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0952c2026" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">讓德歸
<lb ed="K" n="0952c21"/>穹昊</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0952c2103" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">責躬罪己乃仁主之揮謙讓德歸天則先王之盛美尚書云朕躬有罪無
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0953a" n="0953a"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a01"/>以萬方萬方有罪罪在朕躬</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0112" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">精求用粃糠</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0117" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">國家設科取土校藝求人
<lb ed="K" n="0953a02"/>大則經濟之材小則郡牧之識粃糠之者咸預搜羅者歟</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0223" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">殲刑羅狡猾</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a03"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0301" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">殲者盡也國家懲惡勸善發號施令羅籠狡猾之俗盡復淳素之風刑法既眀民人自恱</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a04"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">懸爵待忠良</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0406" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">文德化成武功致治甲乙之利恒設草澤之士無遣
<lb ed="K" n="0953a05"/>以天祿旌其能以三爵秋其序非文行道藝莫可預也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0522" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">風揭旌旗猛</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a06"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0601" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">爾雅曰注旄首曰旌有鈴曰旗天風助動威而不猛其在茲也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0625" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">雲橫醜虜
<lb ed="K" n="0953a07"/>亡</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0702" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">赫矣王師討乎眾虜下合民志上恊天心感雲陣以橫空助兵氣而無或者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0732" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">生
<lb ed="K" n="0953a08"/>靈皆有截</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0805" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">天生蒸民非君不治致於有截之域咸荷無私之化也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a09"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a0901" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">天道助時昌</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a0906" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">皇天無親甘露於是而降惟德是輔太階於是而平得非
<lb ed="K" n="0953a10"/>六府孔脩四聰廣闢</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1009" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">布令施深信</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1014" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">夫令者非信不行是以賞罰折
<lb ed="K" n="0953a11"/>中內外咸遵易曰信及豚魚禮曰和慶行令</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1118" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">憂民軫納隍</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1123" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖人憂民
<lb ed="K" n="0953a12"/>以百姓心為心以百姓欲為欲致黔黎於富壽儻一物失所若巳納之於隍隍溝池也</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953a13"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">除祅揮寶刃</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1306" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">翦除祅孽振耀武功則寶刃一揮而煙塵四息者也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1326" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">蕩
<lb ed="K" n="0953a14"/><g ref="#CB08768">󲉀</g>跨龍驤</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1405" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">蕩平<g ref="#CB08768">󲉀</g>厲<g ref="#CB15210">󳭪</g>廣聖功鵬舉龍驤莫能喻其勢也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1423" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">宵旰
<lb ed="K" n="0953a15"/>綏諸夏</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1504" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖君之布大政也宵分尚衣日旰未食撫綏於諸夏肅靜於萬邦統
<lb ed="K" n="0953a16"/>御寰區親臨大政</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1608" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">勤劬服遠羌</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1613" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">效惟堯之劬瘠美大禹之胼<g ref="#CB04447">𦙁</g>勤勞
<lb ed="K" n="0953a17"/>克彰羌夷遠服披皮辮髮之眾重譯<g ref="#CB06224">󱡐</g>街而來八蠻歸朝四夷向化</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1727" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">狴牢冤
<lb ed="K" n="0953a18"/>枉理</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1803" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">片言折獄之臣盡衣設禁之法固無冤枉不滯狴牢<g ref="#CB05033">䥫</g><g ref="#CB10119">󲞇</g>繡衣得其人矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a1831" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">刑
<lb ed="K" n="0953a19"/>政要威揚</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a1905" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">尚書云刑故無小斯所以不嚴而治也雖彰善瘴惡慎刑政於
<lb ed="K" n="0953a20"/>士師戢暴揚威嚴法令於<g ref="#CB08780">󲉌</g>尉也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953a2014" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">從諫無留滯</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953a2019" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">木從繩則正后
<lb ed="K" n="0953a21"/>從諫則聖萬機之內庶政之間每容及霤之言恒聽沃心之說必使事無留滯聖德日新
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0953b" n="0953b"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0953b01"/>者焉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0103" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">溫恭柔勝剛</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0108" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">剛者天也有雷霆肅殺之威柔者地也有發生厚載
<lb ed="K" n="0953b02"/>之德王者溫恭允塞慈睿仁明以尊賢容眾之恒恩脒雪霜震電之烈政也</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0230" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">親耕
<lb ed="K" n="0953b03"/><anchor xml:id="beg_11e" type="cb-app"/>豐<anchor xml:id="end_11e"/>稼穡</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0304" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">聖主憂民思<anchor xml:id="beg_11f" type="cb-app"/>豐<anchor xml:id="end_11f"/>稼穡表行政化遂致親耕</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0320" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">有瑞集禎
<lb ed="K" n="0953b04"/>祥</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0402" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">咸謌上瑞共樂豐年喜集禎祥河清麟現</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0418" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">金闕來傳詔</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0423" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">皆瞻金闕
<lb ed="K" n="0953b05"/>共仰天書高竪鷄竿恩流遐邇</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0513" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">銀蟾任意望</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0518" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">皎潔銀蟾清光夜朗
<lb ed="K" n="0953b06"/>怡懷杍思吟望不休</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0609" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">戶無扄夜室</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0614" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">國豐人泰盜竊不生月下民謌無扃
<lb ed="K" n="0953b07"/>夜室</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0703" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">海不起波浪</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0708" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">干戈息戰咸謌聖化之功海不揚波以表太平之運</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953b08"/><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">美譽功堪立</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0806" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">恩霑草木惠及昆蟲聖譽彌深堪盡青史</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b0822" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">佳聲
<lb ed="K" n="0953b09"/>孰敢當</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b0904" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">諸國咸<g ref="#CB02082">󰠢</g>戎夷懾伏行無為而化天下施惠愛以保昌期聖德難齊
<lb ed="K" n="0953b10"/>佳聲莫及</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1005" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">輕風搖劒珮</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1010" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">風清御苑日暖彤<g ref="#CB08887">󲊷</g>聖祚方隆梯山入貢君臣
<lb ed="K" n="0953b11"/>道合禮教遐敷衣<g ref="#CB10120">󲞈</g>雜沓以瞻天劒珮丁當而拱極</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1121" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">巧舌似笙簧</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1126" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">謌元
<lb ed="K" n="0953b12"/>百之德詠育物之功頌聲有聞諫諍無用赤心奉上有異笙簧利口雖開難陳謟媚</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1233" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">德
<lb ed="K" n="0953b13"/>重非身老</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1305" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">漁樵遂志草木咸蘇高天莫量重德難比勿以暮年之質皆可
<lb ed="K" n="0953b14"/>欽崇木期敦肅之人彌堪鄭重</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1413" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">生踈欲面墻</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1418" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">事君之道忠信為基淳素
<lb ed="K" n="0953b15"/>之門進取有頼恒存雅橾免致猜嫌理有生踈面墻何異</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1523" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">上林多異菓</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953b16"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1601" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">芳時雨霽上苑花眀鸎遷<g ref="#CB09118">𠳮</g>木之端草嫰危亭之畔生成之煦菓實乖滋</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1629" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">曲水引
<lb ed="K" n="0953b17"/>廻塘</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1703" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">天池浩渺地紀寬通萬<g ref="#CB21113">𣲖</g>朝宗四溟無盡廻塘潤下曲沼流波濟物之功用之
<lb ed="K" n="0953b18"/>莫極</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1803" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">俊利韜機略</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1808" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">徵諸賢哲共作股肱籌略既施寰宇克靜神情高爽
<lb ed="K" n="0953b19"/>利用逢時雅合典經深窮王佐</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b1913" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">忠貞竭胏膓</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b1918" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">衣冠濟濟識量汪汪
<lb ed="K" n="0953b20"/>進退知機忠貞有則力扶宗社能竭肺膓流雅頌於國風列奇姿於麟誾</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953b2029" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">松蘿
<lb ed="K" n="0953b21"/>穿戶牖</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953b2104" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">至仁之御宇也務在安人各從所欲故有志尚清虛心師莊老徑荒
<pb ed="K" xml:id="K35.1259.0953c" n="0953c"/>
<lb ed="K" n="0953c01"/>苔蘚門暎松蘿自謂巢由不臣堯舜優游卒嵗以樂道哉</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953c0123" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">筠色秀琳琅</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953c02"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953c0201" rend="margin-left:1em"><note place="inline">筠色翠綠貞實可愛秀潤之姿尤類美王爾雅云西北之美者有崑崘琳琅玡焉此盖取
<lb ed="K" n="0953c03"/>喻於賢人君子懷玉守莭青蠅不能為玷雪霜豈得其凋邪</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953c0324" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">玉帛堆盈
<lb ed="K" n="0953c04"/>庫</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953c0402" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">易云何以聚人曰財尚書又云民心無常惟惠之懷是以賞功旌德非玉帛而何況
<lb ed="K" n="0953c05"/>今萬國向化四方歸仁<g ref="#CB08887">󲊷</g>實之貢日無暫暇自然堆庫盈府以<g ref="#CB09112">󲎘</g>國用矣</note>。</p></cb:div><cb:div type="orig"><lg xml:id="lgK35p0953c0529" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:0em">軍儲
<lb ed="K" n="0953c06"/>溢太倉</l></lg></cb:div><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pK35p0953c0604" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">連營百萬之旅太倉九年之粟蓋膏腴之田歲稔吴楚之運日至淨
<lb ed="K" n="0953c07"/>漢設常平倉不可同日而語也</note>。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="K" n="0953c08"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="28"><cb:jhead>御製秘藏詮懷感一百韻詩卷第二十八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="K" n="0953c09"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pK35p0953c0901" rend="margin-left:1em">丙午歲高麗國大藏都監奉
<lb ed="K" n="0953c10" type="honorific"/><g ref="#CB30072">𠡠</g>雕造</p></cb:div>
</cb:div></body>
